# Docker Backend — Trading Bot Containerization

## What This Skill Covers
Packaging the trading bot and all its dependencies into Docker containers for reproducible, portable deployment on DigitalOcean. Covers Dockerfile authoring, multi-service compose configuration, volume management, health checks, and container lifecycle management.

